data.description: Looking for a quiet place to retire or raise your children? Take a look at this gorgeous Victorian home on a corner lot on Main St in Canoochee GA! Home features center hallway, hardwood floors, 9 foot ceilings, large front and back porches, storage building that is wired and insulated, chicken coop and custom built kids' treehouse! All appliances stay and sellers will also leave furniture! Call today to schedule your showing!
